OL,3,C'Covid Cruise' passenger worries 72-
OL,4,Chour hantavirus isolation 'not long
OL,5,Cenough'
OL,7,FA woman who was made to isolate for
OL,8,Ftwo weeks just before the global COVID-
OL,9,F19 pandemic has questioned why those
OL,10,Fexposed to the hantavirus outbreak are
OL,11,Fonly being asked to quarantine for
OL,12,Fthree days.
OL,14,FElaine Spencer was on board the
OL,15,FDiamond Princess cruise ship in 2020
OL,16,Fwhen a number of passengers tested
OL,17,Fpositive for COVID-19.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
