FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778533866
OL,3,C'Covid Cruise' passenger worries 72-
OL,4,Chour hantavirus isolation 'not long
OL,5,Cenough'
OL,7,FAfter quarantining on the ship for 16
OL,8,Fdays she was made to isolate at Arrowe
OL,9,FPark Hospital in Liverpool along with
OL,10,Fher fellow passengers.
OL,12,FSix years on, the 60-year-old says
OL,13,Fshe's experiencing "deja vu" as she
OL,14,Fsees new arrivals begin their own
OL,15,Fisolation period at the very same
OL,16,Fhospital.
OL,26,@uD@VrruD@Xqp
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778533866
OL,3,C'Covid Cruise' passenger worries 72-
OL,4,Chour hantavirus isolation 'not long
OL,5,Cenough'
OL,7,FTwenty British passengers were taken
OL,8,Fto isolate at Arrowe Park Hospital on
OL,9,FSunday 10 May 2026. They had been on
OL,10,Fboard the MV Hondius cruise vessel on
OL,11,Fwhich six hantavirus cases have been
OL,12,Fconfirmed.
OL,14,FElaine said that seeing footage of
OL,15,Fpeople arriving at Arrowe Park
OL,16,FHospital brought memories flooding
OL,17,Fback.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778533866
OL,3,C'Covid Cruise' passenger worries 72-
OL,4,Chour hantavirus isolation 'not long
OL,5,Cenough'
OL,7,FShe said: "It makes me realise how
OL,8,Flong ago it was, but actually it was
OL,9,Fjust like yesterday. so yes, it's
OL,10,Fstill there."
OL,12,FRather than isolating for 14 days like
OL,13,FElaine, the new arrivals will be
OL,14,Fquarantined at the hospital for 72-
OL,15,Fhours before beginning their own 45-
OL,16,Fday self-isolation at home.
OL,26,@oD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778533866
OL,3,C'Covid Cruise' passenger worries 72-
OL,4,Chour hantavirus isolation 'not long
OL,5,Cenough'
OL,7,FElaine said: "Personally... I worry.
OL,8,FWe had 14 days on the ship, 14 days at
OL,9,FArrowe Park. We weren't allowed to
OL,10,Fleave, not even our rooms. Trusting
OL,11,Fthe public to self-isolate is a big
OL,12,Fask.
OL,14,F"Maybe it should be more than 72
OL,15,Fhours, but I expect they have close
OL,16,Fmonitoring."
OL,26,@oD@NOUxD@LO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778533866
OL,3,C'Covid Cruise' passenger worries 72-
OL,4,Chour hantavirus isolation 'not long
OL,5,Cenough'
OL,7,FJanelle Holmes, chief executive of
OL,8,FWirral University Teaching Hospital
OL,9,FNHS Foundation Trust, said the 72-hour
OL,10,Fperiod allows time for the patients to
OL,11,Fmake arrangements for their long term
OL,12,Fisolation at home.
OL,14,FShe said: "Ideally, if you're
OL,15,Fisolating for several weeks, you'd
OL,16,Fwant to do that in your own home. This
OL,17,Fperiod gives us time to ensure a safe
OL,18,Ftransition."
OL,26,@vD@KOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39107
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778533866
OL,3,C'Covid Cruise' passenger worries 72-
OL,4,Chour hantavirus isolation 'not long
OL,5,Cenough'
OL,7,FElaine said she faced uncertainty and
OL,8,Ffear while under quarantine at Arrowe
OL,9,FPark Hospital, with the isolation
OL,10,Fperiod taking a mental toll.
OL,12,FShe said: "The first few days were
OL,13,Fpretty traumatic. The accommodation
OL,14,Fwasn't brilliant, but we're here,
OL,15,Fwe're alive. Everything's good,"
OL,26,@tD@KOUwD@`O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39108
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778533866
OL,3,C'Covid Cruise' passenger worries 72-
OL,4,Chour hantavirus isolation 'not long
OL,5,Cenough'
OL,7,F"You want to go home, and the unknown
OL,8,Fis scary. Some people felt like lepers
OL,9,F- taxi drivers refused to take them
OL,10,Fhome. You're brought back, you're
OL,11,Fmonitored, and then you're just let
OL,12,Fgo."
OL,14,FElaine wrote a daily diary during her
OL,15,Ftime at Arrowe Park, which helped her
OL,16,Fprocess the experience and later
OL,17,Fformed the basis of her book "Diamond
OL,18,FQuarantine."
OL,20,FShe said: "If I put it on paper, I
OL,21,Fcould actually get it out of my head."
OL,26,@tD@DO]yD@^OUzD@LO]|D@KOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39109
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778533866
OL,3,C'Covid Cruise' passenger worries 72-
OL,4,Chour hantavirus isolation 'not long
OL,5,Cenough'
OL,7,FHer message to those currently in
OL,8,Fisolation is to trust the medical
OL,9,Fstaff and follow their advice.
OL,11,FShe said "It can be frightening, but
OL,12,Fyou have to trust the medical people.
OL,13,FHopefully, it will not spread."
OL,15,FProfessor Robin May, chief scientific
OL,16,Fofficer at the UK Health Security
OL,17,FAgency (UKHSA), said the passengers
OL,18,Fwill receive constant support both
OL,19,Fduring and after their stay at Arrowe
OL,20,FPark.
OL,26,@sD@JOUuD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G9/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39110
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778533866
OL,3,C'Covid Cruise' passenger worries 72-
OL,4,Chour hantavirus isolation 'not long
OL,5,Cenough'
OL,7,FHe said: "During that period we'll be
OL,8,Fsupporting very closely with ongoing
OL,9,Ftesting, still checking for virus and
OL,10,Fantibodies, but also, of course,
OL,11,Femotionally, because this is clearly
OL,12,Fnot what any of them would have wished.
OL,14,F"We're assessing on a kind of case-by-
OL,15,Fcase basis whether their home is the
OL,16,Fbest place for them, or perhaps, if
OL,17,Fthey live in a very shared
OL,18,Faccommodation, it might need to be
OL,19,Fsomewhere else. And we're discussing
OL,20,Fthat with them."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G10/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39111
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778533866
OL,3,C'Covid Cruise' passenger worries 72-
OL,4,Chour hantavirus isolation 'not long
OL,5,Cenough'
OL,7,FJanelle Holmes said that specialist
OL,8,Fteams are welcoming the guests,
OL,9,Fensuring their safety and comfort
OL,10,Fafter a long and difficult journey.
OL,12,FShe said: "The most important thing is
OL,13,Fto make sure they are safe, welcome,
OL,14,Fand have a chance to rest," she said.
OL,15,F"We distribute welfare packs and
OL,16,Fensure they have means to contact
OL,17,Ffamily and friends.
OL,26,@tD@KOUvD@[O]wD@AOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G11/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39112
SC,0012
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778533866
OL,3,C'Covid Cruise' passenger worries 72-
OL,4,Chour hantavirus isolation 'not long
OL,5,Cenough'
OL,7,F"Guests are being housed in self-
OL,8,Fcontained flats, couples or families
OL,9,Ftogether, single travellers on their
OL,10,Fown - with en suite, kitchen, and
OL,11,Flounge facilities. Upon arrival, they
OL,12,Fare screened and continuously assessed
OL,13,Fby medical teams, with regular welfare
OL,14,Fchecks."
OL,16,FJanelle Holmes stressed "this is not
OL,17,FCOVID" and the risk to the public
OL,18,Fremains very low.
OL,26,@xD@YOU
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G12/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39113
SC,0013
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778533866
OL,3,C'Covid Cruise' passenger worries 72-
OL,4,Chour hantavirus isolation 'not long
OL,5,Cenough'
OL,7,FShe added that Arrowe Park was chosen
OL,8,Ffor its experience with previous
OL,9,Fisolation cases, proximity to
OL,10,FLiverpool's specialist infectious
OL,11,Fdisease facilities, and its self-
OL,12,Fcontained flats.
OL,14,FShe said: "We managed to isolate Wuhan
OL,15,Fand Diamond Princess guests with no
OL,16,Fspread of infection."
OL,26,@vD@KOUxD@UO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G13/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39114
SC,0014
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778533866
OL,3,C'Covid Cruise' passenger worries 72-
OL,4,Chour hantavirus isolation 'not long
OL,5,Cenough'
OL,7,FHolmes praised the rapid response and
OL,8,Fteamwork between local staff and
OL,9,Fpartner agencies, including the
OL,10,Fpolice, fire service, Wirral Council,
OL,11,Fthe UK Health Protection Agency, and
OL,12,FNHS England.
OL,14,FHolmes confirmed, "There's no impact
OL,15,Fon the hospital. Services are running
OL,16,Fas normal, and patients should still
OL,17,Fattend their appointments. The
OL,18,Fhospital is completely separate from
OL,19,Fthe isolation facility."
OL,26,@vD@SOU{D@XO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G14/15
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
