FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39115
SC,0015
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1778533866
OL,3,C'Covid Cruise' passenger worries 72-
OL,4,Chour hantavirus isolation 'not long
OL,5,Cenough'
OL,7,FAs the new arrivals settle in, Holmes
OL,8,Fthanked all involved and reassured the
OL,9,Fpublic that Wirral's response is
OL,10,Ffocused on professionalism, safety,
OL,11,Fand compassion.
OL,13,FReporting History sees journalists
OL,14,Fjoin News At Ten anchor Tom Bradby to
OL,15,Frevisit their remarkable on-the-day
OL,16,Freports of the defining events of the
OL,17,Fmodern age. Listen to the episodes
OL,18,Fbelow...
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}     G15/15
